T1  - Central Counterparty Exposure in Stressed Markets
AU  - Huang, Wenqian
AU  - Menkveld, Albert J.
AU  - Yu, Shihao
Y1  - 2020/08/06
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3601
