T1  - Making Marketplaces Safe: Dominant Individual Rationality and Applications to Market Design
AU  - Roth, Benjamin N.
AU  - Shorrer, Ran I.
Y1  - 2020/12/08
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3643
