T1  - Vertical Contracts in a Supply Chain and the Bullwhip Effect
AU  - Qu, Zhan
AU  - Raff, Horst
Y1  - 2020/10/15
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3630
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3630
